<abstract><t>The 6rd [RFC5969] linktype does not support IPv6 link-local addressing, multicast and 6rd nodes are off-link from each other. The host configuration protocol DHCPv6 [RFC3315] relies on link-local addressing and multicast to function.  This document specifies how DHCPv6 can be used across a 6rd link.</t></abstract>

